<!-- ══════ WORKFLOW ══════ -->
<section id="workflow">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="eyebrow">The workflow</div>
    <h2>Drop a file. Curate the events. <em>Export the figure.</em></h2>

    <div class="workflow">
      <div class="steps">
        <div class="step">
          <div class="n">01</div>
          <div><h4>Open a recording</h4><p>Drag an <span class="mono">.abf</span> or <span class="mono">.dat</span> into the workspace. The group → series → sweep tree builds itself; protocols, channel units and timestamps come along.</p></div>
        </div>
        <div class="step">
          <div class="n">02</div>
          <div><h4>Pick an analysis window</h4><p>Cursors, Resistance, I–V, AP, Events, Bursts, Field PSP, Paired — same shape every time. Continuous-mode viewer, draggable cursors, parameter sidebar, results table.</p></div>
        </div>
        <div class="step">
          <div class="n">03</div>
          <div><h4>Review &amp; curate</h4><p>Sweep-by-sweep with detected events highlighted. Accept, reject, re-fit, add or remove by click. Optional <span class="mono">train grouping</span> labels closely-spaced events as <span class="mono">T1, T2…</span>.</p></div>
        </div>
        <div class="step">
          <div class="n">04</div>
          <div><h4>Export &amp; archive</h4><p>Publication-ready SVG / PDF / PNG figures. CSV / Excel / Prism summary tables. A <span class="mono">.tracer</span> sidecar next to the recording — every selection, cursor and parameter, restored on reopen.</p></div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="wf-visual">
        <div class="win-title">
          <span class="dot-row"><span></span><span></span><span></span></span>
          <span>session log · cell_a2.dat</span>
          <span class="sp"></span>
          <span class="ct">events · live</span>
        </div>
        <div class="body">
          <div class="wf-file">
            <span class="led ok"></span>
            cell_a2.dat · 412 MB · 128 sweeps · HEKA Patchmaster
          </div>
          <div class="wf-arrow">↓</div>
          <div class="wf-file">
            <span class="preset-k">window</span>
            Event Detection · template match · biexp fit
          </div>
          <div class="wf-arrow">↓</div>
          <div class="wf-result">
<span class="mute">▸</span> <span class="hl">open</span>      cell_a2.dat<br>
<span class="mute">▸</span> <span class="hl">tree</span>      Group 02 · Series 04 · 32 sweeps<br>
<span class="mute">▸</span> <span class="hl">detect</span>    142 events · template · σ = 4.0<br>
<span class="mute">▸</span> <span class="hl">review</span>    138 accepted · 4 rejected · 2 re-fit<br>
<br>
<span class="ok">✓</span> <span class="path">events.csv</span>           <span class="mute">142 rows · per-event</span><br>
<span class="ok">✓</span> <span class="path">events.svg</span>           <span class="mute">trace + ticks</span><br>
<span class="ok">✓</span> <span class="path">cell_a2.dat.tracer</span> <span class="mute">sidecar saved</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="metrics">
      <div class="metric"><div class="n">14</div><div class="l">Analysis windows</div></div>
      <div class="metric"><div class="n">50<em>+</em></div><div class="l">Native file formats</div></div>
      <div class="metric"><div class="n">0</div><div class="l">Lines of code required</div></div>
      <div class="metric"><div class="n">100<em>%</em></div><div class="l">Offline · on-device</div></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

